# 60c6a2d9a4fe4b09a0296ae70e2700e0
msgid "Let’s being by reviewing what we the inputs and outputs of InaSAFE - **hazard**, **exposure**, and **impact**.  These terms are important for you to remember because the analysis process will always depend on these three things."
